UID:bEtnCukifsQEFFNTM07iO
SUMMARY:Outdoor festival
DTSTAMP:20260317T213915Z
DTSTART:20260328T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Issaquah (15 miles SE)\n\nSpring into Adventure typically inclu
	des a 3k walk\, yoga\, art\, adoptable dogs\, kids’ activities\, food truc
	ks\, and 40 vendors at Lake Sammamish State Park\, 2000 NW Sammamish Road 
	in Issaquah. Donation. Parking is $10 if you don’t have a Discover Pass.\n
