	ies\\) Hosted at Eastlake High School\, Sammamish\, WA Join the community 
	for an exciting Math Fair happening on: March 29\, 2026 ⏰ 12:00 PM – 5:00 
	PM 400 228th Ave NE\, Sammamish\, WA 98074 This annual event \\(organized 
	by Washington State Math Association – WSMA\\) brings students together to
	 showcase math projects in a fun\, science-fair–style format. ━━━━━━━━━━━━
	━━━━━━ THEME: Structures & Systems Students explore how mathematical struc
	tures power real-world applications — engineering\, architecture\, compute
	r systems\, and more! ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ COMPETITION DIVISIONS • Grades 3–
	5 • Grades 6–8 Teams of 1–4 students Projects can include trifolds\, poste
	rs\, models\, or demonstrations Awards will be given in each division. ━━━
